* Goals Overview

  The Classpath Plugin has one main goal:

  * {{{./classpath-mojo.html}classpath:classpath}} is recommended to bound
  to the <<generate-resources>> phase and is used to add different jar libs
  (e.g. non-maven jars) to classpath of your project.

